{"tid":1716012,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【何必趕盡殺絕】許廷鏗黑白相加歌詞觸動大陸網民 被屈港獨狂鬧","createTime":"2019-11-13T08:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:14:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb5a795496d12947361dfe6e1afc559846ab10d","tid":1716012,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:37:37.000Z","msg":"瘋警昨日向中文大學狂發千枚催淚彈，網傳他們今日將轉移陣地，轉攻香港大學，關心學生們的網民不停轉發相關消息，提醒大家都要小心。<br />\n作為港大畢業生，身份既是歌手又是牙醫的許廷鏗（Alfred），昨日就在社交網上載一張黑白照，並留下新歌《偽人》一串歌詞「圍牆有耳，浮雲有眼。沿途有舌，而誰有力。若是暴露我的真，我擔心你轉身。若是暴露我的真，我擔心，冒犯眾生。」<br />\n雖然Alfred未有說明甚麼，但網民都似乎收到他的「心意」，紛紛留意答謝他。Alfred亦同時在IG動態放了一張以深灰色底配上淺灰色字的文字圖，寫上「何必趕盡殺絕 心疼」。<br />\n不過，當汽水罐都可變成滅火筒，足見甚麼「種類」的人，看同一件事都會有不同看法，由於Alfred將歌詞及黑白照同時上載到微博，即時觸動到大陸網民的「玻璃心」，不斷留言罵他是港獨份子，又斥他藉歌詞撐暴徒，有人更留言叫他以後不要用微博，滾回香港等等。而Alfred所屬華納唱片公司就表示沒有任何回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191113/large/1573630290_4fa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573630290_4fa0.jpg&h=b5009551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191113/large/1573630288_3bf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573630288_3bf2.jpg&h=74987807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191113/large/1573630290_f67b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573630290_f67b.jpg&h=3a8dbbbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191113/large/1573630292_fa02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191113%2Flarge%2F1573630292_fa02.jpg&h=305e0dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191113/60262047\" data-s